sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Patient
  participant Home as "/home"
  participant Index as "/requests"
  participant Detail as "/requests/:requestId"
  participant Bundle as "PatientRequestReturnBundle"
  participant Placeholder as "Governed child placeholder"

  Patient->>Home: Opens patient shell
  Home->>Home: Render PatientSpotlightDecisionProjection or PatientQuietHomeDecision
  Home->>Index: Open requests from single dominant action
  Index->>Bundle: Persist selectedFilterRef and selectedAnchorRef
  Patient->>Index: Focus request row
  Index->>Detail: Enter or click selected RequestSummaryRow
  Detail->>Bundle: Reuse lineageTupleHash and continuityEvidenceRef
  Detail->>Detail: Render RequestLineageStrip and RequestDetailHero
  Detail->>Placeholder: Focus more-info, callback, records, communications placeholders
  Placeholder-->>Detail: State remains placeholder-only until owner projection lands
  Detail->>Index: Return to requests
  Index->>Bundle: Restore selected row focus target
  Bundle-->>Index: Browser back and refresh replay keep same anchor
